divs: Sighting DetailsI am reporting this event on behalf of the person you took the photo. It is hard to tell what the shape is, but it appears that it is not an airplane and based on the description from the owner of the picture, it was not an airplane. Also, it seems like there have been other reports of a similar object in Wyoming. It is possible that the object is a UAV of some sort, but it is not one that is public knowledge? Hopefully the shape can be identified. It was reported as silver in color and that is what appears to be the case in the photos. The object has been seen more than one time in the same area.
